#

Spiced Chicken Biryani with Saffron and Cashew Nuts

$15.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

Nuts (if using cashews)Dairy (if using yogurt)

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinNut-Free Option AvailableGluten-Free Option Available

Tags:

Indian CuisineComfort FoodOne-Pot MealFestive Dish

Description

A fragrant and flavorful one-pot dish combining tender chicken, fragrant basmati rice, and aromatic spices, topped with a touch of saffron and crunchy cashews.

Ingredients

  • Basmati Rice: 2 cups
  • Chicken Thighs: 1.5 lbs
  • Onion: 2 medium, sliced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • Green Chilies: 2, slit
  • Yogurt: 1 cup
  • Saffron Threads: 1/4 tsp, soaked in 2 tbsp warm milk
  • Cashew Nuts: 1/2 cup, toasted
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Mint Leaves: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Garam Masala: 1 tsp
  • Turmeric Powder: 1/2 tsp
  • Cumin Seeds: 1 tsp
  • Black Cardamom: 1
  • Cloves: 3
  • Cinnamon Stick: 1 small
  • Bay Leaf: 1
  • Salt: to taste
  • Oil: 3 tbsp
